<title>Converting Gravitational Potential Energy to Kinetic Energy</title>
<para id="fs-id1169084544136">Starting from rest, a <emphasis effect="bold">222 kg</emphasis> block slides down a frictionless incline from a height of <emphasis effect="bold">7.2 m</emphasis>. Find the velocity when it hits the ground. Study the problem and its solution in this video.</para>
