 </m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{Δ"KE"= {  {1}  over  {2} }  ital "mv" rSup { size 8{2} }  -  {  {1}  over  {2} }  ital "mv" rSub { size 8{0}   rSup { size 8{2} } } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math>. Thus,</para><equation id="eip-90"><m:math>
