              <m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{v rSub { size 8{f} } = sqrt {2 ital "gh"+v rSub { size 8{0}   rSup { size 8{2} } } } = sqrt {2 \( 9 "." "80"" m/s" rSup { size 8{2} }  \)  \(  - 0 "." "180"" m" \) + \( 2 "." "00 m/s" \)  rSup { size 8{2} } } =0 "." "687"" m/s"} {}</m:annotation>
